Rattrap:


Rattrap fell into the water, flipping a few times under. Despite the 
damage, he struggled the best he could to get back up to the surface. 
Being a 400 pound robot wasn't making things easy. He pushed his arms 
and kicked his legs. 

His head finally made it to the surface. He was afraid he would be 
drug back under the water because of his own weight. And neither was 
the water any good to his sytems.
